Privacy Notice for Inkrypt Videos
Introduction
Welcome to Inkrypt Videos, available at inkryptvideos.com. This privacy policy outlines how we, Inkrypt Videos (“InkryptVideos” or “We”), collect, use, and protect your personal information when you interact with our services.
By using our platform to upload videos or access your account, you acknowledge and agree to this privacy policy. If you are registered for an account, have access to your organization’s account, or are responsible for managing or paying for an account, you are considered a Subscriber (referred to as “you”).
Cookies and Their Usage
Cookies are small text files stored on your device by websites you visit. They help websites remember your actions and preferences.
We use cookies to maintain your session on InkryptVideos. By continuing to use our website, you agree to our use of cookies. If you prefer not to use cookies, you may disable them through your browser settings, but this may affect your ability to use certain features of our site.
Information We Collect
When you sign up for InkryptVideos, we request your name and email address. Your email serves as your primary point of contact and is used for authentication purposes.
We also use web analytics tools to gather anonymized, aggregated data on user interactions with our website. This data helps us understand user behavior, such as time spent on our site, links clicked, and content preferences, enabling us to improve our services.
In accordance with the EU’s General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), you may request the deletion of your personal data. This option is available to all our users, including those outside the EU.
Video Playback Data Collection
We collect anonymized and aggregated data on video playback, such as the number of unique viewers and the popularity of specific videos, and technical data about any issues in playbacks. This information helps content creators analyze user engagement and enhance their offerings. For instance, if a particular video is frequently watched, it may indicate its importance or complexity, prompting the creator to produce supplementary content.
How We Protect Your Data
Your privacy is important to us. We do not share your personal information with third parties. We will not send you unsolicited emails, but we may send you important updates and news related to InkryptVideos.
Communication
We collect your email address to communicate with you regarding your account and to send updates about our services. By signing up, you agree to receive such communications electronically. You may unsubscribe at any time by contacting us at
info@inkryptvideos.com
.
Compliance with GDPR
The General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) grants EU citizens the right to know what personal data websites collect about them and to request its deletion or correction. We are committed to transparency and will gladly assist you with any GDPR-related inquiries or requests. Please reach out to us at
info@inkryptvideos.com
for further information.
Use of Google APIs
InkryptVideos utilizes Google APIs to access your Google Drive files and obtain your email address. By using our services, you agree to the following:
We access and display your Google Drive files and folders to provide an overview of your stored content.
We download your Google Drive files to facilitate video streaming and playback on our platform.
We collect your Google Drive email address to ensure proper authentication and communication.
Your Google Drive data is used solely for these purposes and is not shared with third parties. We adhere to Google’s API Services User Data Policy, including the Limited Use requirements.
Data Security Measures
We prioritize the security of your data and implement the following measures:
Encryption:
All data transmitted between our servers and your device is encrypted using SSL/TLS protocols.
Access Control:
Only authorized personnel have access to user data, and we regularly update our access controls to maintain security.
Data Storage:
We store your data on secure servers protected by firewalls and other security measures.
Regular Audits:
We conduct routine security audits to identify and mitigate potential risks.
User Control:
You have the right to access, modify, or delete your data at any time by contacting us at
info@inkryptvideos.com
.
